 class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-10" style="opacity:0"><div class="bg-background border border-border p-6 py-4 rounded-2xl" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)"><div class="relative space-y-5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-coins border rounded-xl shadow-sm p-2"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="6"></circle><path d="M18.09 10.37A6 6 0 1 1 10.34 18"></path><path d="M7 6h1v4"></path><path d="m16.71 13.88.7.71-2.82 2.82"></path></svg><div class="rounded-lg border text-card-foreground border-none shadow-none leading-relaxed tracking-normal bg-inherit"><div class="p-0"><h3 class="leading-[32px] font-ivyora text-2xl mb-1 tracking-[-0.72px]">New ways for readers to support you</h3><p class="text-base text-muted-foreground">Let readers support you, signal they were early, and share in your growth.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="bg-background border border-border p-6 py-4 rounded-2xl" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)"><div class="relative space-y-5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-megaphone border rounded-xl shadow-sm p-2"><path d="m3 11 18-5v12L3 14v-3z"></path><path d="M11.6 16.8a3 3 0 1 1-5.8-1.6"></path></svg><div class="rounded-lg border text-card-foreground border-none shadow-none leading-relaxed tracking-normal bg-inherit"><div class="p-0"><h3 class="leading-[32px] font-ivyora text-2xl mb-1 tracking-[-0.72px]">Reach more readers</h3><p class="text-base text-muted-foreground">Grow your audience by sharing seamlessly across social &amp; more.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="bg-background border border-border p-6 py-4 rounded-2xl" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)"><div class="relative space-y-5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-lock border rounded-xl shadow-sm p-2"><rect width="18" height="11" x="3" y="11" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path></svg><div class="rounded-lg border text-card-foreground border-none shadow-none leading-relaxed tracking-normal bg-inherit"><div class="p-0"><h3 class="leading-[32px] font-ivyora text-2xl mb-1 tracking-[-0.72px]">Own your audience &amp; writing</h3><p class="text-base text-muted-foreground">No more platform-dependent followers - readers can subscribe via email or wallet.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="scroll-snap-section bg-background"><div class="bg-background py-24"><div class="container"><h2 class="font-ivyora flex-1 tracking-tight text-primary text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl max-w-2xl text-center mx-auto" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(-20px)">Ideas that matter</h2><p class="text-base text-muted-foreground mt-4 max-w-2xl text-center w-full mx-auto" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)">Read the voices driving today&#x27;s most important conversations.</p></div><div class="pt-8 sm:pt-12"><!--$?--><template id="B:29"></template><!--/$--></div></div></section><section class="scroll-snap-section bg-background"><div class="bg-background h-full w-full flex flex-col justify-center py-12 space-y-4 md:space-y-12 px-4"><div class="container mx-auto text-center"><h2 class="font-ivyora flex-1 tracking-tight text-primary text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl max-w-2xl text-center mx-auto" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(-20px)">From crypto to cooking, &amp; everything in between</h2><p class="text-base text-muted-foreground mt-4 max-w-2xl text-center w-full mx-auto" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)">Discover what writers, thinkers, and storytellers are talkin