/div></div></section><section class="scroll-snap-section bg-background"><div class="h-full w-full flex flex-col justify-center py-12 relative" aria-labelledby="cta-heading"><div class="container mx-auto"><div class="shadow-2xl max-w-7xl overflow-hidden inset lg:h-[640px] bg-primary mt-16 lg:mt-0 rounded-xl pt-16 lg:pl-16" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px)"><div class="h-full flex flex-col lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-rows-none gap-8 lg:gap-12"><div class="flex flex-col gap-4 px-6 lg:px-0 lg:pb-16 justify-center items-center lg:items-start text-center lg:text-left lg:gap-8 flex-1 lg:max-w-full max-w-xl mx-auto" style="opacity:0"><div class="flex flex-col gap-4 lg:gap-5"><h2 class="font-ivyora flex-1 tracking-tight text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl max-w-2xl text-center lg:text-left text-primary-foreground mx-0" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(-20px)">A better place for ideas to grow</h2></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-10 items-center lg:items-start"><p class="text-primary-foreground/80 text-base sm:text-lg" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)">We&#x27;re building a new model for writing, one powered by readers directly supporting the writers that inspire them, that they believe in.<br/><br/>No paywalls or subscription treadmills. No algorithms deciding your worth. Just readers who can support the writing they love.</p><div class="group"><div class="liquid-glass-wrapper liquid-glass-pill gap-1 liquid-glass-cobalt liquid-glass-blur-minimal"><div class="liquid-glass-visual-layers" style="transform-origin:50% 50%;transform:none"><div class="liquid-glass-effect"></div><div class="liquid-glass-tint"></div><div class="liquid-glass-shine"></div></div><div class="liquid-glass-content"><button class="font-sans inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap rounded-xl text-sm font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 h-10 px-4 py-2 text-inherit hover:bg-transparent hover:text-inherit" type="button" disabled="">Sign in<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-right ml-1 h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5"><path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div><div class=" flex  w-full xs:w-2/3 lg:w-full lg:h-full pl-6 lg:pl-0 pr-6 justify-end items-end mx-auto " style="opacity:0;transform:scale(0.95)"><img alt="Paragraph collector dialog showing how readers can collect a post" loading="lazy" width="1080" height="1126" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-tl-lg w-full h-auto justify-end self-end" style="color:transparent" srcSet="https://img.paragraph.com/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,width=1080,quality=85/https://paragraph.com/_next/static/media/collector_dialog.0h98gn1z56wfv.png 1x, https://img.paragraph.com/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,width=3840,quality=85/https://paragraph.com/_next/static/media/collector_dialog.0h98gn1z56wfv.png 2x" src="https://img.paragraph.com/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,width=3840,quality=85/https://paragraph.com/_next/static/media/collector_dialog.0h98gn1z56wfv.png"/></div></div></div></div></div></section></main><footer class="bg-background py-16 lg:py-24" role="contentinfo" aria-label="Site footer"><div class="container px-6 mx-auto flex flex-col gap-12 lg:gap-16"><div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-12 w-full text-center" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)"><div style="opacity:0;transform:scale(0.8)"><a aria-label="Go to homepage" href="/"><img alt="Paragraph" loading="lazy" width="40" height="40" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/static/media/wordmark_black.0qv7o33p_ji2k.svg 1x, /_next/static/media/wordmark_black.0qv7o33p_ji2k.svg 2x" src="/_next/static/media/wordmark_black.0qv7o33p_ji2k.svg"/></a></div><nav class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-c