both people and agents react, make calls, and see outcomes settle quickly. It’s basically a training ground to understand how intelligent agents behave, how they coordinate, and how onchain systems might work when humans and AI operate side by side.\"},{\"id\":\"pHAshSx8bisCrfs1oLpg\",\"name\":\"Assetux\",\"url\":\"@assetux\",\"description\":\"Mine Bitcoin with microtasks on Telegram.\\nAccess $BTC on TON Blockchain.\\nSpend across millions of merchants worldwide.\"},{\"id\":\"1HSqvpNyUtEWO2fzI5PB\",\"name\":\"Taiko Labs\",\"url\":\"@taiko-labs\",\"description\":\"An Ethereum Based Rollup.\"},{\"id\":\"uQL4WRZHmhEYDGbLsew3\",\"name\":\"FOLIO\",\"url\":\"@folio\",\"description\":\"Sharing updates about FOLIO, an Opinion Polling Platform for Crowd-Forecasting, Gamified Market Research, and Daily Rewards.\"},{\"id\":\"zJER49fvUqTKIIVtiKZs\",\"name\":\"GranFondo Riviera Nayarit News\",\"url\":\"@granfondo-riviera-nayarit\",\"description\":\"Experience the Sand to Sun cycling fiesta in Mexico.\"},{\"id\":\"RL7LKMOiT9Yg2AQmj8fq\",\"name\":\"News from RBC GranFondo\",\"url\":\"@rbcgranfondo\",\"description\":\"North America's biggest Gran Fondo, open to all.\"},{\"id\":\"0etmlkv2oPdpZS0tQvAA\",\"name\":\"Reef Chain News\",\"url\":\"@reefchain\",\"description\":\"Reef Chain is laying the foundations for everyone to own their financial future.\"},{\"id\":\"zCRl2qIrZoJRb6V3meBs\",\"name\":\"DHK dao\",\"url\":\"@dhk\",\"description\":\"Web3 公民教育 | Civic education for web3.\"},{\"id\":\"4st52QCsAEiTJlAUYqAD\",\"name\":\"Horizen Blog\",\"url\":\"@horizenofficial-2\",\"description\":\"Powering privacy-first and regulatory-ready infrastructure for the new digital economy.\"},{\"id\":\"qlHp1SWHwgTpbL2HHu6P\",\"name\":\"The BSCN Debrief\",\"url\":\"@bscnalpha\",\"description\":\"The 48-Hour Market Debrief: a twice-weekly newsletter published on BSCN's Paragraph.xyz channel, recapping the most important crypto stories from the prior 48 hours.\"},{\"id\":\"dZrlXrAD2EP7vL1JVvxk\",\"name\":\"What Wilson Heard\",\"url\":\"@hanverstraete.eth\",\"description\":\"A blog by recidivist founder Han Verstraete with ideas and thoughts how to author your life in Web3 and beyond.\"},{\"id\":\"ZWHS1hLpSpGhcs0pyRvM\",\"name\":\"Devcon newsletter\",\"url\":\"@efevents\",\"description\":\"Sign up to receive updates about Devcon, the flagship event of the Ethereum Foundation. Devcon 8 will take place in Q4 2026 in Mumbai, India.\"},{\"id\":\"cmjKmyFr4kNegz0J3NX8\",\"name\":\"talent\",\"url\":\"@talent\",\"description\":\"Giving builders the recognition they deserve.\"},{\"id\":\"IKDVsi66g4EvJgIBcQiH\",\"name\":\"AyaHQ\",\"url\":\"@ayahq\",\"description\":\"Stay connected and up to date with the latest developments in the AyaHQ ecosystem.\"},{\"id\":\"hL46JQWFi70m23hOjl96\",\"name\":\"Bakaka\",\"url\":\"@bakaka\",\"description\":\"This publication explores the intersection of crypto, artificial intelligence, the open web, and agentic networks. I write from the perspective of someone focused on infrastructure, real-world adoption, and systems that scale beyond hype. Topics range from blockchain payment rails and stablecoins to AI coordination, autonomous agents, and the networks that will power the next phase of the internet, especially in emerging markets. The goal is simple: thoughtful analysis, grounded opinions, and practical insight into where technology is actually heading.\"},{\"id\":\"4HOP5zMeZOx2TSE1rJ8X\",\"name\":\"Onchain @ Zerion\",\"url\":\"@zerion\",\"description\":\"Get product updates on Zerion Wallet \u0026 Zerion API.\"},{\"id\":\"hz3uBrCFnWjUGxouCxXT\",\"name\":\"GCR\",\"url\":\"@globalcoinrsrch\",\"description\":\"Global Coin Research (GCR) is a Community of Investors \u0026 Researchers.\"},{\"id\":\"WTlBnRUBpkCSWsHSykOu\",\"name\":\"Safecast\",\"url\":\"@safecast\",\"description\":\"Updates from Safecast on how open environmental data empowers citizens and communities worldwide.\"},{\"id\":\"rrhd9WXLWLjVjmy5g6jY\",\"name\":\"Poster.fun\",\"url\":\"@poster\",\"description\":\"Curated news from best of Onchain + Ai + cc0 based remix dApps.\"},{\"id\":\"mRzqbIuYwOlMAG2nYLvY\",\"name\":\"Proof of PortCo\",\"url\":\"@mhventures\",\"description\":\"Proof of Portco is MH Ventures’ monthly pulse check on the builders we back. Each issue serves as onchain style “proof” of real progress: rapid-fire founder Q\u0026A, milestone highlights, key asks, and the latest episodes from our Dealflow Podcast. Proof of Portco keeps investors, founders, and friends in the loop, showing exactly how our portfolio is compounding momentum, one verifiable update at a time.\"},{\"id\":\"1pqFXMYxoSWSsfxCK7E4\",\"name\":\"Chainbase Network - Blog\",\"url\":\"@chainbase\",\"description\":\"The Hyperdata Network built to transform fragmented blockchain signals into structured, verifiable, and AI-ready data, enabling permissionless coordination between agents, apps, and humans in a unified data economy.\"},{\"id\":\"jNPBs0jsZSJcxFw7blH2\",\"name\":\"Officer's Blog\",\"url\":\"@officercia\",\"description\":\"Threat Researcher \u0026 Author.\"}],\"logoMap\":{\"RiSgH90rlXboE2f3FnSK\":{\"small\":\"$L29\",\"large\":\"$L2a\"},\"D9YJuccLaKARzB7O0MJf\":{\"small\":\"$L2b\",\"large\":\"$L2c\"},\"mHhMUnidiw8XXZJFVryh\":{\"small\":\"$L2d\",\"large\":\"$L2e\"},\"cN0u09vE5TyjBMqA9I7F\":{\"small\":\"$L2f\",\"large\":\"$L30\"},\"BMV6abfvCSUl51ErCVzd\":{\"small\":\"$L31\",\"large\":\"$L32\"},\"malkJGtn0mhXnWaNejzt\":{\"small\":\"$L33\",\"large\":\"$L34\"},\"pHAshSx8bisCrfs1oLpg\":{\"small\":\"$L35\",\"large\":\"$L36\"},\"1HSqvpNyUtEWO2fzI5PB\":{\"small\":\"$L37\",\"large\":\"$L38\"},\"uQL4WRZHmhEYDGbLsew3\":{\"small\":\"$L39\",\"large\":\"$L3a\"},\"zJER49fvUqTKIIVtiKZs\":{\"small\":\"$L3b\",\"large\":\"$L3c\"},\"RL7LKMOiT9Yg2AQmj8fq\":{\"small\":\"$L3d\",\"large\":\"$L3e\"},\"0etmlkv2oPdpZS0tQvAA\":{\"small\":\"$L3f\",\"large\":\"$L40\"},\"zCRl2qIrZoJRb6V3meBs\":{\"small\":\"$L41\",\"large\":\"$L42\"},\"4st52QCsAEiTJlAUYqAD\":{\"small\":\"$L43\",\"large\"